    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Justice was done",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.64,
      "endTime": 10.55
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The word 'justice' is given two different meanings in the text.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.56,
      "endTime": 15.27,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What is the distinction between them?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.28,
      "endTime": 19.84,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "What",
            "label": "疑问词"
          },
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The word justice is usually associated with courts of law.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 19.85,
      "endTime": 25.48,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We might say that justice has been done when a man's innocence or guilt has been proved beyond doubt.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 25.49,
      "endTime": 33.14,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "that",
            "label": "指示代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Justice is part of the complex machinery of the law.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.15,
      "endTime": 37.74,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "is",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Those who seek it, undertake an arduous journey and can never be sure that they will find it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 37.75,
      "endTime": 44.87,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          },
          {
            "text": "that",
            "label": "指示代词"
          },
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Judges, however wise or eminent, are human and can make mistakes.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 44.88,
      "endTime": 51.17,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "are",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "There are rare instances when justice almost ceases to be an abstract concept.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.18,
      "endTime": 58.15,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "are",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Reward or punishment are meted out quite independent of human interference.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.16,
      "endTime": 64.29,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "are",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          }
        ],
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "At such times, justice acts like a living force.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "endTime": 69.43,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When we use a phrase like 'it serves him right',",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 69.44,
      "endTime": 73.5,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "we are, in part, admitting that a certain set of circumstances has enabled justice to act of its own accord.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 73.51,
      "endTime": 83.83,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "are",
            "label": "谓语/系动词"
          },
          {
            "text": "that",
            "label": "指示代词"
          },
          {
            "text": "its",
            "label": "形容词性物主代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When a thief was caught on the premises of a large jewellery store one morning,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 83.84,
      "endTime": 89.47
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the shop assistants must have found it impossible to resist the temptation to say 'it serves him right'.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.48,
      "endTime": 97.66,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          },
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The shop was an old converted house with many large, disused fireplaces and tall, narrow chimneys.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 97.67,
      "endTime": 106.06,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          },
          {
            "word": "House",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "房子"
          },
          {
            "word": "Tall",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "高的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Towards midday, a girl heard a muffled cry coming from behind one of the walls.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 106.07,
      "endTime": 112.85
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "As the cry was repeated several times,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112.86,
      "endTime": 115.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "she ran to tell the manager who promptly rang up the fire brigade.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 115.79,
      "endTime": 121.36
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The cry had certainly come from one of the chimneys,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 121.37,
      "endTime": 124.64
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "but as there were so many of them, the firemen could not be certain which one it was.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 124.65,
      "endTime": 132.24,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They located the right chimney by tapping at the walls and listening for the man's cries.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 132.25,
      "endTime": 139.66,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "After chipping through a wall which was eighteen inches thick,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 139.67,
      "endTime": 144.22
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "they found that a man had been trapped in the chimney.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 144.23,
      "endTime": 148.39,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "that",
            "label": "指示代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "As it was extremely narrow, the man was unable to move,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 148.4,
      "endTime": 153.2,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "it",
            "label": "人称代词/主语"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but the fire fighters were eventually able to free him by cutting a huge hole in the wall.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 153.21,
      "endTime": 160.9
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The sorry-looking, blackened figure that emerged,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 160.91,
      "endTime": 164.97,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "that",
            "label": "指示代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "admitted at once that he had tried to break into the shop during the night but had got stuck in the chimney.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 164.98,
      "endTime": 173.21,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [
          {
            "text": "that",
            "label": "指示代词"
          }
        ],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He had been there for nearly ten hours.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 173.22,
      "endTime": 177.24
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Justice had been done even before the man was handed over to the police.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 177.25,
      "endTime": 182.25,
      "analysis": {
        "grammar": [],
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
